{"tid":373083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"部分澳豬既政治潔癖又發作","createTime":"2017-08-24T17:59:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T03:38:12.000Z","uid":43189,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ff6bf1128ce6ca0db130d9d19f01d8b2fbfd07fc","tid":373083,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:59:16.000Z","msg":"嗱講明係部分，有少數澳門人都仲係識諗既<br />\n<br />\n話說堂前燕寫咗篇嘢，講明今次係制度問題，結果有啲豬又開始發作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/r1r.patpat/photos/a.244815128941123.54413.242997322456237/1452930714796219/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fr1r.patpat%2Fphotos%2Fa.244815128941123.54413.242997322456237%2F1452930714796219%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=Npv5wDLWnBRp1i3akIOPzp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=169c46d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/r1r.patpat/photos/a.244815128941123.54413.242997322456237/1452930714796219/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9ghr6ey1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9ghr6ey1&h=b2ebcecc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/47ymblu3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F47ymblu3&h=4127c9d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/q7sdmzpr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fq7sdmzpr&h=a4d6cc8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/sp59qx42\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsp59qx42&h=38a60408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n基本上有啲豬既思維係民生同政治係分開既，到你搞完民生仲會搞政治嗎？<br />\n<br />\n呢位港豬就另外貼堂<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lrh06wx5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flrh06wx5&h=ed212de1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9092febad1cb57b19bc9c053ab3faa2ce35acdb","tid":373083,"uid":15249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedB